@left_context
new-page: true

= SLD Starting Context

The SLD begins with parliamentary representation and residual regional structures, but the post-communist party brand is weak. Twój Ruch is fading, PPS/UP are junior partners, and Razem is not yet a playable identity in this slice.

The 2014-2015 objective is not ideological triumph. It is survival.

- @library: Back to library.

@voter_model
new-page: true

= Voter Model

Support is calculated from Polish voter segments rather than Weimar class blocks. The first playable slice tracks urban professionals, urban working-class voters, rural east and west, religious practice, age cohorts, women, LGBTQ voters, and the Belarusian/eastern minority segment.

Party Affairs cards move specific segments, then the monthly loop recalculates national polling and threshold safety.

